msgstr "Het betalingsproces is begonnen in een nieuwe venster."

#: pretix_multisafepay/templates/pretix_multisafepay/redirect.html:20
msgid "The window to enter your payment data was not opened or was closed?"
msgstr ""
"Het venster om uw betaling in te voeren is niet geopend of was gesloten?"

#: pretix_multisafepay/templates/pretix_multisafepay/redirect.html:25
msgid "Click here in order to open the window."
msgstr "Klik hier om het venster te openen."

#: pretix_multisafepay/views.py:143 pretix_multisafepay/views.py:151
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We had trouble communicating with MultiSafepay. Please try again and get "
#| "in touch with us if this problem persists."
msgid ""
"We had trouble communicating with Multisafepay. Please try again and get in "
"touch with us if this problem persists."
msgstr ""
"Wij hadden problemen in de communicatie met MultiSafepay. Probeer het "
"opnieuw en neem contact met ons op als dit probleem aanhoudt."

#: pretix_multisafepay/views.py:206
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "We received your payment but were unable to mark your ticket as the "
#| "server was too busy. Please check beck in a couple of minutes."
msgid ""
"We received your payment but were unable to mark your ticket as the server "
"was too busy. Please check back in a couple of minutes."
msgstr ""
"We hebben uw betaling ontvangen, maar konden uw ticket niet als betaald "
"markeren, omdat de server overbelast was. Kom over een paar minuten terug."

#: pretix_multisafepay/views.py:215
msgid ""
"We received your payment but were unable to mark your ticket as paid as one "
"of your ordered products is sold out. Please contact the event organizer for "
"further steps."
msgstr ""
"We hebben uw betaling ontvangen maar konden uw ticket niet markeren als "
"betaald, aangezien een van uw bestelde producten uitverkocht is. Neem "
"contact op met de organisator van het evenement voor verdere instructies."

#: pretix_multisafepay/views.py:231
msgid ""
"Sorry, there was an error in the payment process. Please check the link in "
"your emails to continue."
msgstr ""
"Sorry, er heeft zich een fout voorgedaan in het betalingsproces. Klik op de "
"link in uw e-mails om door te gaan."

